title: Eintracht Frankfurt (women) - Wikipedia
snippet: Eintracht Frankfurt is a German women's association football club based in Frankfurt. Its first team currently plays in the German top flight, Frauen-Bundesliga. From 1998 to 2020, the club was known as 1. FFC Frankfurt.

title: Bundesliga-Fußball mit Eintracht Frankfurt, Frauen | FRANKFURT.DE - DAS OFFIZIELLE STADTPORTAL
snippet: Im Stadion am Brentanobad an der Ludwig-Landmann-Straße residiert das Eintracht Frankfurt Frauenteam, Fußball-Bundesligist, bis 2020 unter dem Namen 1. FFC Frankfurt mehrfacher deutscher Meister und Champions-League-Sieger 2015.

title: 1. FC Frankfurt - Wikipedia
snippet: 1. Fußballclub Frankfurt (Oder) E. V. e. V., commonly known as 1. FC Frankfurt, is a German football club based in Frankfurt (Oder), Brandenburg. The club was founded as the army club SV VP Vorwärts Leipzig in Leipzig in East Germany in 1951.
